Title: What's Happening Inside the NIH and NSF
Oracle justified its JavaScript trademark with Node.js—now it wants that ignored
Description: Oracle filed a motion to dismiss in response to Deno’s petition to cancel its “JavaScript” trademark. But instead of addressing the real issue—that JavaScript is an open standard with multiple independent implementations—Oracle is trying to stall the process and sidestep accountability.

Title: Introducing Apple Invites, a new app that brings people together
Description: Apple today introduced Apple Invites, a new app for iPhone that allows users to create custom invitations to gather friends and family.
